casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, BY the COMMISSIONER OF TRANSPORTATION, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
CHERRY HILL MITSUBISHI, INC., a New Jersey Corporation, et al., Defendants/Third-Party Plaintiffs,
and
Foulke Management Corporation, a New Jersey Corporation, d/b/a Cherry Hill Triplex, Cherry Hill Dodge, Cherry Hill Kia and Cherry Hill Mitsubishi, Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Victor Akpu, the Commissioner of the Department of Transportation, Third-Party Defendant-Respondent. C-36 September Term 2018
081180 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005198-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
